data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4 bedroom, 3-bathroom home with 3 car garage and RV parking located in a cul de sac! This meticulously maintained home showcases beautiful upgrades throughout. There is a separate formal living room, a family room & formal dining room. Vaulted ceilings that enhances its spacious feel & ceiling fans throughout, and beautiful views of the garden from the kitchen. All bedrooms are located upstairs and equipped with ceiling lights & fans. The backyard includes a covered patio, custom built deck & gazebo, and a swimming pool. The following items were replaced: water heater, pool filter, AC units, and furnace. Easy access to the freeway and in close proximity to stores and restaurants. Schedule your showing today!
